159 #if !defined(REG_READ32)
160  #define REG_READ32(address) (*(volatile uint32_t*)(address))
161 #endif
162 
166 #if !defined(REG_WRITE32)
167  #define REG_WRITE32(address, value) ((*(volatile uint32_t*)(address))= (uint32_t)(value))
168 #endif
169 
173 #if !defined(REG_BIT_SET32)
174  #define REG_BIT_SET32(address, mask) ((*(volatile uint32_t*)(address))|= (uint32_t)(mask))
175 #endif
176 
180 #if !defined(REG_BIT_CLEAR32)
181  #define REG_BIT_CLEAR32(address, mask) ((*(volatile uint32_t*)(address))&= ((uint32_t)~((uint32_t)(mask))))
182 #endif
183 
188 #if !defined(REG_RMW32)
189  #define REG_RMW32(address, mask, value) (REG_WRITE32((address), ((REG_READ32(address)& ((uint32_t)~((uint32_t)(mask))))| ((uint32_t)(value)))))
190 #endif

732  __IO uint32_t MPRA;

739  __IO uint32_t OPACR[AIPS_OPACR_COUNT];

4427 #define ERM_EARn_COUNT 2u
4428 
4430 typedef struct {
4431  __IO uint32_t CR0;
4432  uint8_t RESERVED_0[12];
4433  __IO uint32_t SR0;
4434  uint8_t RESERVED_1[236];
4435  struct { /* offset: 0x100, array step: 0x10 */
4436  __I uint32_t EAR;
4437  uint8_t RESERVED_0[12];
4438  } EARn[ERM_EARn_COUNT];
4439 } ERM_Type, *ERM_MemMapPtr;

7171 #define LPIT_TMR_COUNT 4u
7172 
7174 typedef struct {
7175  __I uint32_t VERID;
7176  __I uint32_t PARAM;
7177  __IO uint32_t MCR;
7178  __IO uint32_t MSR;
7179  __IO uint32_t MIER;
7180  __IO uint32_t SETTEN;
7181  __IO uint32_t CLRTEN;
7182  uint8_t RESERVED_0[4];
7183  struct { /* offset: 0x20, array step: 0x10 */
7184  __IO uint32_t TVAL;
7185  __I uint32_t CVAL;
7186  __IO uint32_t TCTRL;
7187  uint8_t RESERVED_0[4];
7188  } TMR[LPIT_TMR_COUNT];
7189 } LPIT_Type, *LPIT_MemMapPtr;

7394 typedef struct {

7396  __I uint32_t PARAM;

7399  __IO uint32_t SR;

7401  __IO uint32_t DER;
7402  __IO uint32_t CFGR0;
7403  __IO uint32_t CFGR1;

7405  __IO uint32_t DMR0;
7406  __IO uint32_t DMR1;
7407  uint8_t RESERVED_2[8];
7408  __IO uint32_t CCR;
7409  uint8_t RESERVED_3[20];
7410  __IO uint32_t FCR;
7411  __I uint32_t FSR;
7412  __IO uint32_t TCR;
7413  __O uint32_t TDR;
7414  uint8_t RESERVED_4[8];
7415  __I uint32_t RSR;
7416  __I uint32_t RDR;
7417 } LPSPI_Type, *LPSPI_MemMapPtr;

8752 #define MPU_EAR_EDR_COUNT 5u
8753 #define MPU_RGD_COUNT 16u
8754 #define MPU_RGDAAC_COUNT 16u
8755 
8757 typedef struct {
8758  __IO uint32_t CESR;
8759  uint8_t RESERVED_0[12];
8760  struct { /* offset: 0x10, array step: 0x8 */
8761  __I uint32_t EAR;
8764  __I uint32_t EDR;
8767  } EAR_EDR[MPU_EAR_EDR_COUNT];
8768  uint8_t RESERVED_1[968];
8769  struct { /* offset: 0x400, array step: 0x10 */
8770  __IO uint32_t WORD0;
8771  __IO uint32_t WORD1;
8772  __IO uint32_t WORD2;
8773  __IO uint32_t WORD3;
8774  } RGD[MPU_RGD_COUNT];
8775  uint8_t RESERVED_2[768];
8776  __IO uint32_t RGDAAC[MPU_RGDAAC_COUNT];
8779 } MPU_Type, *MPU_MemMapPtr;

12095  __IO uint32_t FPCAR;
